[CHARACTERIZATION - 7/10] [ART - 10/10] [STORY - 7/10] [IMPACT - 6/10] [FAPABILITY - 5/10] For a manga that really only features 2 characters, it utilizes them well and you can appreciate the dynamic between the daughter and father. Although it unfortunately pulls the overused "boo-hoo I raped my daughter" schtick with the dad at the end, the dedication of Karin to her dad and her determination outweighs and compensates for it. The story is straightforward but compelling due to the circumstances of the characters and its effort in acknowledging the social stigma around incest. Coupled with the stunning art that arguably approaches serialized manga levels, this work leaves many disgusted, confused, aroused, or a combination of all. Due to the sole sex scene leaning on the shorter side with an emotional build-up and sweet ending, some might forego busting a nut to this in favor of savoring the feelings. Still, those who like a quick, intense, and thrilling fap won't be disappointed.
